nodes.text: An unidentified Dyclops pirate served as a gunner aboard the Blood Brother, a starship commandeered by the notorious pirate Reddjak. As a minion of Reddjak, that Dyclops was part of the Red Fury Brotherhood. In the early years of the Galactic Empire, he or she was arrested along with his crewmates by order of Zell, former Republic Space Ranger and ambassador of Majoor.
